articles.title: Princess Anne leaves hospital after treatment for minor injury - BBC.com
articles.description: The Princess Royal was taken to hospital after she sustained minor injuries thought to have been caused by a horse.
articles.content:
The Princess Royal has returned home from hospital, where she was being treated for a minor head injury and concussion.
